The Caretaker is located somewhere in near the Foundry Deck in Udûn.\n\nDefeat the Caretaker.
A thundering yell can be heard from somewhere near the Foundry Deck in Udûn.
With all the clanging of machines you have caused a herd of goats, who were peacefully hiding out in the broken machines, to look elsewhere for food and shelter.
Goats can be found in Udûn.\n\nYou should shoo away goats.

It seems you have made quite a lot of noise, with all your tinkering. There must have been a herd of goats seeking shelter in the broken machines. Now they graze the valley floor and if you do not intervene, they will make their way towards supplies at the Udûn Foothold.
